            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680013401118-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Brush a little <strong>cold water</strong> around the edges of the pizza base (this will help to seal the dough!)</p><p>Fold the <strong>pizza base</strong> over the filling and seal firmly by pinching the dough together along the join, making sure there are no gaps – these are your <strong>calzones</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680013404392-x200.jpg",
